data.description: A wonderful place that truly feels like home! The mature trees adding to the curb appeal and the blank slate of the house offer a great opportunity for personalization and creating lasting memories.    The emphasis on natural light with the window in the entryway is a lovely touch, and having a designated space for displaying photos or art adds character and warmth to the home. The flexibility of the flex space allows for various uses, whether it be for work, dining, or relaxation.    The vaulted ceilings in the oversized living area contribute to the spacious and airy atmosphere, making it an inviting space for gatherings and everyday living. And the eat-in kitchen, with its open concept design, provides not only functionality but also a sense of togetherness while preparing meals.    Having the owner suite on the first floor offers convenience and privacy, and the luxurious features like the tub, glass shower, and large walk-in closet create a retreat-like experience. Meanwhile, the secondary bedrooms upstairs and the additional flex space provide plenty of room for family or guests, as well as opportunities for entertainment and relaxation.    Outside, the large fully fenced backyard offers a private and secure space for outdoor activities, whether it's hosting BBQs or enjoying leisurely summer evenings. It sounds like a place where many wonderful memories can be made, and where you can truly enjoy the comforts of home. The community has two amenity centers and will be adding a third with another pool and gym. Redbird Ranch does lots of community events! BRAND NEW CARPET AND PAINT THROUGHOUT.
